Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.09,0:00:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.76,0:00:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.22,0:00:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wali kelas kita ngajarnya lama, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.98,0:00:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin bahas
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.89,0:00:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}soal wisata kelulusan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.15,0:00:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah enggak sabar.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.23,0:00:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.03,0:00:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia bersikap biasa saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.15,0:00:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Normal banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.99,0:00:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik, kita lanjutkan
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.24,0:00:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sesuai rencana ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.37,0:00:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian bebas menentukan\Ntujuan grup masing-masing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.91,0:00:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, coba pikirkan\Npilihan kalian sendiri dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.00,0:00:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan kamarnya nanti.\NKita tentukan pembagian grup
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.13,0:00:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Arc Wisata Kelulusan dimulai!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.39,0:02:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, ini kan
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.31,0:02:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}seharusnya tugas pengurus kelas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.85,0:02:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lebih baik kita kerjakan sama-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.19,0:02:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku cuma mau main stapler besar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.94,0:02:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada-ada saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.25,0:02:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf ya, Nishi, kau jadi ikut bantu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.46,0:02:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.38,0:02:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya aku suka pekerjaan\Nyang diulang-ulang begini.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.84,0:02:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau baik sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.13,0:02:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serius,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.17,0:02:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}apa alasan "kegiatan klub" itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.71,0:02:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memangnya itu alasan biar bisa bebas tugas?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.01,0:03:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kegiatan klub sepenting itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.51,0:03:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau enggak bisa, jangan jadi pengurus.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.34,0:03:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cuma buat cari nilai sikap saja, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.60,0:03:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku benci orang
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.01,0:03:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang cuma pura-pura baik di luar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.93,0:03:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selagi mereka asyik\Nmenikmati hidup enak,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.77,0:03:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mereka enggak pernah\Nmemikirkan beban orang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.06,0:03:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hon, tenanglah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.23,0:03:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Akan kutunjukkan video lucu\N- Lalu dia perlahan berbalik
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.36,0:03:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- dan mengatakan ini.\N- yang kutonton kemarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.61,0:03:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata ulahmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.82,0:03:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku enggak paham maksudnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.53,0:03:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nishi, ada kabar baik akhir-akhir ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.53,0:03:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tadi katanya mau bahas video?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.45,0:03:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku penasaran,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.62,0:03:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}apa ada kemajuan dengan Yamada?\NKatanya kau enggak mengerti
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.21,0:03:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}perasaanmu sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.33,0:03:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soal itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.09,0:03:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.84,0:03:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian kerjakan ini berdua saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.30,0:03:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yamada!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.22,0:03:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kalian malah teriak?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pasti repot kalau cuma berdua.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.05,0:03:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada sekitar delapan orang mengerjakan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.35,0:03:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah itu terlalu banyak?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.46,0:03:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makanya aku enggak ngapa-ngapain sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.23,0:03:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada-ada saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.31,0:03:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, bantu kami saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.06,0:03:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serahkan padaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.27,0:03:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertama, tolong lipat kertas di sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.52,0:03:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siap!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.61,0:04:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk grup,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}lebih baik diundi\Natau pilih sendiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja pilih sendiri lebih baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.95,0:04:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pasti banyak yang berpikir begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.25,0:04:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Melihat ukuran grupnya,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.16,0:04:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bisa jadi kita dapat\Nanggota grup yang canggung.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.46,0:04:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana menurutmu, Tani?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.45,0:04:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.38,0:04:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa maksudnya "ya"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.17,0:04:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau enggak menyimak, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa suasananya begini?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.93,0:04:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka lagi bertengkar?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.47,0:04:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di kelas kalian,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.89,0:04:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sejauh mana\Nrencana wisata kelulusannya,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.77,0:04:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}selain kegiatan grup?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.98,0:04:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami baru menentukan grup.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.23,0:04:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selanjutnya, kami akan tentukan\Ntujuan masing-masing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.98,0:04:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu lebih cepat dari kelas kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.19,0:04:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.95,0:04:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nishi jadi lebih cerewet dari sebelumnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.74,0:04:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suasananya lumayan bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.78,0:04:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baguslah, Nishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.37,0:04:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anggaplah
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.29,0:04:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku enggak ada di sini sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.66,0:04:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kelas Gapacho sudah bahas\Nkegiatan grup.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.96,0:04:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cepat banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.38,0:05:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hon, tolong aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.84,0:05:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan pura-pura enggak tahu apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.34,0:05:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Aku enggak tahu apa-apa".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.88,0:05:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski aku berusaha keras
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.13,0:05:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}melanjutkan percakapan ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.30,0:05:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku bisa mendengar detak jantungku.\NAku bisa gila.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.14,0:05:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski aku senang, kuharap waktu ini
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.98,0:05:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bisa cepat berlalu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.94,0:05:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selesai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian berdua cepat banget, sampai seram.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.15,0:05:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biar kubawa ini ke ruang guru.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.28,0:05:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biar kubantu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.78,0:05:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak, kau duduk saja terus di sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.66,0:05:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biar aku saja yang beranjak dari kursi ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.41,0:05:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.38,0:05:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus cari topik pembicaraan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.93,0:05:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Klub marching band latihan keras, ya.\N- Matahari terbenam lebih cepat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.43,0:05:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Iya.\N- Iya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.94,0:06:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.94,0:06:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soal kegiatan grup\Nsaat wisata kelulusan nanti,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.24,0:06:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kalau grupmu sudah tentukan tujuan,\Nberi tahu aku diam-diam, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.33,0:06:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.41,0:06:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau tanya begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.16,0:06:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.50,0:06:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.58,0:06:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lebih terus terang saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.80,0:06:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku paham.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.34,0:06:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sopan sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.35,0:06:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lo? Ke mana Yamada?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.06,0:06:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia pulang duluan sama teman sekelasnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.31,0:06:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga, maaf ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.14,0:06:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau enggak perlu menungguku,\Nkau bisa pulang dengannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.90,0:06:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak, otakku sudah mau meledak.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.27,0:06:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sampai kelihatan lemas begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.13,0:06:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, kau sudah yakin sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.94,0:06:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yamada, dari mana saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.82,0:06:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bantu kelas sebelah tadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku merasa cuma aku\Nyang memikirkan wisata ini hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.45,0:06:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Payah banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.50,0:06:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}banyak pasangan yang kumpul-kumpul\Nsebelum wisata kelulusan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.79,0:07:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masa, sih?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin karena ada waktu luang\Nuntuk hal seperti itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.59,0:07:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jaga bicaramu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.13,0:07:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}di waktu luang nanti?\NApa yang bakal kalian lakukan
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.64,0:07:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami harus ngapain, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.31,0:07:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.22,0:07:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau masih bersikap begini\Ndi depan Tani?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.60,0:07:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Bersikap apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.06,0:07:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tingkahmu aneh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.27,0:07:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tingkahku...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.65,0:07:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hari ini memang lagi aneh saja, tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.19,0:07:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aneh apanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.65,0:07:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku biasanya lebih pintar dari ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.03,0:07:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani bahkan sampai tertawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.95,0:07:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.41,0:07:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki, aku mau menghabiskan\Nwaktu luangku bersamamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.29,0:07:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mendadak banget!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.20,0:07:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagus, Tani!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.96,0:07:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.87,0:07:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mantap!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.17,0:07:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silakan dilanjut.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.75,0:07:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki dan Tani bertingkah aneh hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.63,0:07:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masa, sih?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.21,0:07:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau mereka enggak bilang apa-apa,\Nbiarkan saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.63,0:07:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.68,0:07:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita mau pulang bareng begini?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.06,0:08:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau mampir ke minimarket.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.35,0:08:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Duluan, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.02,0:08:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh juga. Enaknya beli apa, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.07,0:08:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Azuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.20,0:08:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hai, pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.70,0:08:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pagi, Kawasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.58,0:08:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk kegiatan grup wisata kelulusan,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.04,0:08:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kalian sudah tentukan tujuan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.16,0:08:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Belum, bikin grup saja belum.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.58,0:08:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lambat banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami sudah putuskan banyak hal tadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.54,0:08:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah capek.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.46,0:08:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekelas pada pasang aura\N"jangan rusak suasana dengan ngomong".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.84,0:08:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak ada yang berani kasih pendapat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.04,0:08:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu,\Nmau diundi saja buat grupnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.27,0:08:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, ayo kita undi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.73,0:08:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada tempat yang mau kalian kunjungi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.52,0:08:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak ada.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.73,0:08:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak, ke mana saja boleh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.19,0:08:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayolah, setidaknya\Nkasih pendapat kalian!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.49,0:08:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian bilang begitu, tapi nanti ngeluh\Nkalau kuputuskan sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.49,0:08:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pilihan, keputusan, pendapat!\NJangan pada malas begitu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.91,0:09:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sabar...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.25,0:09:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sabar...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.37,0:09:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semangat, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.29,0:09:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk grup,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.84,0:09:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}atau pilih sendiri?\Nmenurutmu lebih baik diundi
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.38,0:09:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja pilih sendiri lebih baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.51,0:09:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejujurnya, menurutku lebih baik diundi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.64,0:09:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk wisata kelulusan ini,\Nkarena semua lamban,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.68,0:09:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku mau semuanya cepat selesai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.77,0:09:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah kuduga! Pantas saja\Nkelas kita terasa sangat lamban.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.48,0:09:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertama, putra dan putri membentuk\Ngrup isi dua atau tiga orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.23,0:09:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, grup putra dan putri
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.61,0:09:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}akan digabung\Njadi grup isi lima atau enam orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.49,0:09:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bebas banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.99,0:09:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.53,0:09:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dua atau tiga orang...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.87,0:09:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.41,0:09:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada yang sisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.17,0:09:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa dia paham maksudku?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.76,0:09:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak boleh empat orang, Pak?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.89,0:09:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.18,0:10:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, boleh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.10,0:10:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gampang banget!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.01,0:10:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Diskusikan saja sendiri
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.39,0:10:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan cepat selesaikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.48,0:10:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pada akhirnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.94,0:10:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hore!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.94,0:10:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya aku sudah beli
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.94,0:10:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}majalah wisata.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.07,0:10:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mantap!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.65,0:10:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah situasinya enggak jadi
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.57,0:10:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}harus peduli padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.70,0:10:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.99,0:10:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa enggak apa-apa setiap hari cuma\Nkhawatirkan hal sepele begini?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.42,0:10:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejak masuk SMA,\Nlingkaran pertemanan ini kurang jelas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.09,0:10:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biar bisa berbaur di mana saja,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.42,0:10:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku jaga jarak agar enggak terlalu\Nbergantung pada siapa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.47,0:10:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena lebih gampang\Nmain sama satu atau dua orang saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.01,0:10:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meskipun begitu,\Napa lingkup pertemananku terlalu kecil?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.56,0:10:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Salam kenal, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.47,0:10:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu dari SMP mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bukannya pemalu,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.81,0:10:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi aku terlalu berhati-hati\Nsampai jadi aneh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.57,0:10:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bisa ngobrol bebas sama Taira\Ntanpa perlu jaim.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.36,0:11:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan ngomong santai begitu denganku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.57,0:11:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa tiba-tiba begini?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.66,0:11:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku cuma penasaran\Nkenapa gampang banget ngobrol sama kamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.04,0:11:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.87,0:11:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja kelihatan begitu di matamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.67,0:11:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soalnya enggak ada alasan buat gugup.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.80,0:11:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Bagaimana kalau aku ngomong begini?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.63,0:11:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Aku mau kasih kesan yang bagus."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.17,0:11:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Daripada dengan orang yang mengharuskanmu\Njaga sikap dan jarak,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.38,0:11:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jauh lebih santai bareng orang
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.10,0:11:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang enggak masalah kalau kau berbuat salah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.26,0:11:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku enggak tahu\Napa kau peduli soal hal semacam itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.56,0:11:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.56,0:11:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu berarti...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.73,0:11:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku seperti meremehkanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.27,0:11:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memang begitu, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.73,0:11:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi memang benar...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.07,0:11:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masuk akal juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.66,0:11:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.87,0:11:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku enggak meremehkanmu, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.54,0:11:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gugup...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.25,0:11:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soal apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.25,0:11:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Duluan ya, aku harus berangkat kerja.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.96,0:11:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oke, semangat kerjanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.59,0:12:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang kutakutkan, sih?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.30,0:12:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Azuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.26,0:12:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hari Sabtu kau luang?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.10,0:12:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi bahas apa, nih?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.14,0:12:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tanya apa dia mau jalan hari Sabtu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.64,0:12:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh, ayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.10,0:12:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bisa ikut, Azuma?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.94,0:12:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku naksir dia.\NBisa bantu aku, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.49,0:12:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Azuma, kau tahu aku suka dia, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.95,0:12:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bantu saja dia. Kita kan teman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.46,0:12:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, aku juga enggak keberatan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.21,0:12:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku cuma dimanfaatkan,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.76,0:12:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan meski sadar,\Naku tetap ikut saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.76,0:12:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.14,0:12:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}itu sudah enggak penting sekarang, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.06,0:12:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau soal itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:13:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kurasa ide dan pendapatku sendiri\Nmemang kurang saat itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.65,0:13:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pilihan, keputusan, pendapat!\NJangan pada malas begitu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.61,0:13:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kawasaki, kau benar banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.33,0:13:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Azuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.37,0:13:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, kerja bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.79,0:13:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nabe, Sato, ini bukan arah pulang\Nkalian, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.79,0:13:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami mau belanja
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.79,0:13:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kebutuhan buat wisata kelulusan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.21,0:13:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena searah, ayo bareng.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.68,0:13:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku jarang lewat sini,\Njadi rasanya agak beda.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.97,0:13:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katanya ada toko taiyaki baru\Ndi depan stasiun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.52,0:13:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nanti kita mampir bareng, yuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.72,0:13:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukannya kau baru makan bakpao manis?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.39,0:13:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beda dong,\Nkan ada ruang khusus buat makanan manis!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Mana ada, aku baru dengar.\N- Aku boleh ikut kalian belanja juga?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.77,0:13:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Asyik, ayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.94,0:13:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami mau ke apotek.\NAda apotek langganan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.28,0:13:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rencananya mau ke apotek\Ndi depan patung itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.70,0:13:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.61,0:13:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}apotek di pintu selatan stasiun\Nbarangnya lebih lengkap.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.16,0:13:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau beli pembersih wajah\Nsama toner ukuran travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.99,0:13:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Azuma, ada rekomendasi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.41,0:13:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa enggak pindahkan produk biasamu\Nke botol travel saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.96,0:13:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.92,0:13:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin di hotel juga sudah disediakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.75,0:14:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau dipikir-pikir,\Nini pertama kalinya kita
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.30,0:14:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bisa lihat wajah asli Azuma tanpa makeup.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.67,0:14:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku jadi enggak sabar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.72,0:14:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga lumayan penasaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.47,0:14:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukannya bakal sama saja,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.55,0:14:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi wajahku enggak selucu itu,\Njadi jangan terlalu berharap.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.05,0:14:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudnya apa, sih?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.82,0:14:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka bertiga akhirnya makan taiyaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.53,0:14:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seru banget!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.95,0:14:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kembali!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.33,0:14:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wisata kelulusan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.50,0:14:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wisata Kelulusan Hari 1:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.33,0:14:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aktivitas Pengalaman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.29,0:14:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah semuanya, kumpul\Nsesuai grup kegiatan masing-masing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.80,0:14:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku lebih suka bikin wagashi
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.67,0:14:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}daripada bikin tembikar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.84,0:14:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lebih enak kalau kita bisa\Nbawa pulang hasilnya, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.01,0:14:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pengalaman bikin wagashi ini\Nhasil kemenangan suit kami!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.43,0:14:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami juga makan jatah mereka yang kalah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.93,0:14:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan singkirkan kami begitu saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.22,0:14:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian cuma boleh makan buatan sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.48,0:15:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.56,0:15:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.11,0:15:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu temannya Yamada yang cantik!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.28,0:15:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pasangan luar biasa\Nyang diceritakan Nishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.53,0:15:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami boleh duduk di depanmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.95,0:15:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.28,0:15:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Halo. Maaf kami ikut gabung di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.08,0:15:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Halo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.04,0:15:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Manis banget!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cepat duduk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.91,0:15:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gadis yang menarik.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.58,0:15:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Caranya begini...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.79,0:15:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Instrukturnya kelihatan gampang bikinnya,\Ntapi ternyata susah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.42,0:15:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau jago banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.84,0:15:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Latihan diam-diam, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.05,0:15:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mana ada.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.64,0:15:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terus kenapa bisa jago?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.43,0:15:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Kenapa apanya?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.47,0:15:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Aku cuma ikuti contohnya."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.69,0:15:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, jadi begitu sifat aslinya.\NPaham sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.89,0:15:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Hah?\N- Maaf, kelepasan bicara.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.31,0:15:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh ya, kelasmu besok ke mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.61,0:15:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau enggak salah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.74,0:15:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini rute wisata kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.82,0:15:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar, kan, Hon?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.49,0:15:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada beberapa rute yang sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.58,0:15:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin kita bakal papasan nanti.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.83,0:15:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.20,0:15:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana kalau ketemuan di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau ke sana! Setuju!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.75,0:16:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Ide bagus.\N- Aku sih, enggak keberatan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.50,0:16:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.54,0:16:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hore!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.63,0:16:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anak ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.09,0:16:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dia sengaja menyesuaikan rute Nishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.55,0:16:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau kita papasan,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.47,0:16:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku mau foto bareng, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.84,0:16:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.27,0:16:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau Kelas 1 mandi duluan,\Nberarti Kelas 7 yang terakhir, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.98,0:16:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Main kartu yuk sambil nunggu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.40,0:16:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh juga main game klasik.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.61,0:16:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bahkan bawa domino.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.24,0:16:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tumben banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.07,0:16:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.11,0:16:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau pacaran sama Tani?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.24,0:16:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.24,0:16:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian baru tahu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.49,0:16:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski kalian kelihatan sering bareng,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.37,0:16:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}orang-orang pada enggak sadar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.46,0:16:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami penasaran apa beneran jadian.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.04,0:16:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Habisnya, kalau Suzuki berduaan sama cowok,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.34,0:16:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kesannya biasa saja, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.05,0:16:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masa sih?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.05,0:16:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa yang nembak duluan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.93,0:16:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gimana awalnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.22,0:16:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian sering ngobrol bareng?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.97,0:16:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Banyak banget
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.26,0:16:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang mau kutanyakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.52,0:17:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi nostalgia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.60,0:17:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau kelihatan profesional banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.27,0:17:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hubungan kalian sudah sejauh mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.94,0:17:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.84,0:17:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berani banget kau tanya begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.81,0:17:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian ngapain saja
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.23,0:17:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}waktu dipanggil di festival budaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.06,0:17:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terus...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.23,0:17:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa Tani punya keinginan khusus?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.49,0:17:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah, parah, tokonya tutup!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.31,0:17:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sembunyi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.45,0:17:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}hubungan kami...\NDitanya sudah sejauh mana
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.28,0:17:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hal-hal seru yang kalian bayangkan itu
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.99,0:17:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sama sekali belum terjadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.57,0:17:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kelas 7, waktunya mandi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.34,0:17:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau dipikir-pikir, selama ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.71,0:17:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya aku yang selalu
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.63,0:17:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mulai duluan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.68,0:17:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kadang dia juga pegang tanganku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.26,0:17:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi jujur saja,\Naku ingin dia lebih proaktif.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.23,0:17:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kalau Suzuki berduaan sama cowok,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.69,0:17:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kesannya biasa saja, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.86,0:17:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa karena aku terlalu memancarkan\Naura "enggak punya niat romantis"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.32,0:17:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.19,0:17:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di situ rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.32,0:17:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Azu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.74,0:17:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa?\NKenapa mukamu serius banget?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.95,0:18:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin hubunganku ada kemajuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.62,0:18:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.16,0:18:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gimana bilangnya, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.58,0:18:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau daya tarik yang seperti itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.75,0:18:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sudah cukup manis, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.84,0:18:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tipe manis yang kau maksud
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.46,0:18:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mungkin beda sama yang kuinginkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.39,0:18:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi enggak ada gunanya buru-buru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.43,0:18:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Proses menuju ke sananya itu yang seru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.14,0:18:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pelan-pelan saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.77,0:18:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.35,0:18:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku mau cepat ciuman.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.53,0:18:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ciuman...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.99,0:18:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisa enggak aku jadi sepertimu\Ndan punya aura "cewek anggun"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.12,0:18:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku bukan wanita yang sehebat itu.\NEnggak juga, kalau boleh jujur,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.37,0:18:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silau sekali... Tolong...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.04,0:18:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pintar banget\Nkau bawa pengering rambut sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.17,0:18:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Alis Azuma kelihatan agak beda.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.18,0:19:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ada cara biar aku
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.60,0:19:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bisa temui Tani dengan rambut lembut,\Nberkilau sehabis mandi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.10,0:19:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak bisa kau tahan sampai pagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.73,0:19:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bentar saja, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.31,0:19:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa bakal papasan di pintu, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.77,0:19:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau dia lihat penampilan alamiku
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.69,0:19:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sehabis mandi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.02,0:19:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini sih jelas penampilan "tanpa makeup"\Nyang memaksakan diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.16,0:19:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan lihat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.07,0:19:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lah, kenapa kalian harus malu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.78,0:19:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak perlu disembunyikan kali.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.87,0:19:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau ngeledek aku, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.20,0:19:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lo? Tani di mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.66,0:19:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bawa kuncinya,\Njadi dia pasti masih di dalam.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.71,0:19:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.68,0:19:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kata Yamada,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.13,0:19:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau mungkin ada di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menurutmu aku kelihatan beda\Ndari biasanya, enggak?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.89,0:19:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku kaget.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.93,0:19:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berhasil?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.02,0:19:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tiba-tiba dia kasih jawaban idamanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.81,0:19:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kukira tadi orang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.27,0:19:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mengagetkanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.19,0:19:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata dia kaget beneran.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.23,0:19:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku lega ternyata itu kau.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.73,0:19:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.28,0:20:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh ya,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.57,0:20:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau dapat kamar bareng
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.41,0:20:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}anak-anak yang berisik, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.62,0:20:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau baik-baik saja? Lucu banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.74,0:20:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan tertawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.33,0:20:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka seru banget main kartunya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.25,0:20:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau ikut main?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.25,0:20:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku enggak tahu aturannya,\Njadi cuma nonton.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.42,0:20:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lumayan juga,\Nsuasana cowok-cowok konyol begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.42,0:20:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kau yang dulu\Npasti menolak ikut-ikutan,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.17,0:20:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}entah itu soal teman sekamar\Natau main bareng.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.51,0:20:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.34,0:20:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Atau mungkin iya, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.39,0:20:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.89,0:20:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.97,0:20:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setahun lalu, aku enggak bisa bayangkan\Nberbaur dengan banyak orang begini.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.56,0:20:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mana yang lebih seru?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.27,0:20:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa ini bukan soal\Nmana yang lebih baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.32,0:20:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.48,0:20:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena sebelumnya aku enggak ada keluhan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.24,0:20:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.16,0:20:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}itulah yang kusukai darinya
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.45,0:20:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sejak awal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.99,0:20:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi sekarang...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.00,0:20:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku jadi punya keraguan dan kekhawatiran\Nyang takkan ada kalau aku sendirian.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.34,0:20:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berkat itu,\Naku jadi sadar akan beberapa hal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.55,0:21:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin ada hal lainnya juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.97,0:21:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku senang\Naku enggak mengabaikan hal itu sepenuhnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.10,0:21:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan salah satunya? Dua-duanya bagus?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.39,0:21:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena itulah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.35,0:21:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku bersyukur bisa bertemu denganmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.40,0:21:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.53,0:21:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal sampai tadi,\Npikiranku penuh niat kotor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.83,0:21:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku malu banget!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.05,0:21:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yusuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.64,0:21:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku cinta banget sama kamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.48,0:21:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Miyu.\N- Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.73,0:21:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saatnya balik ke kamarku!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.15,0:22:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dah! Sampai besok!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.52,0:22:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bersenang-senanglah di kamarmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.61,0:22:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak usah buru-buru.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.29,0:22:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Malam hari pertama pun tiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.62,0:22:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku enggak sabar menanti hari esok.
